{"tid":1805684,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔該全部聽朝印啲文宣出去街派","createTime":"2019-12-31T17:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T13:01:47.000Z","uid":21493,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d1e74d59395f8d413e49b63ed4542e1f1c5c2c","tid":1805684,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T17:57:36.000Z","msg":"見有啲區有人派文宣<br />\n<br />\n人哋都做到<br />\n<br />\n我哋一樣得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uyu6TV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uyu6TV.jpg&h=d3f2c8ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A81HHsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA81HHsg.jpg&h=a9180f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrueyyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrueyyX.jpg&h=7b983e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dNckdY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dNckdY.jpg&h=dfa8f2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/My9qFd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMy9qFd0.jpg&h=3f56308a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是日傍晚一行數人於康城派發近千張文宣，真誠希望大家參與民陣舉行的1月1日大遊行，因明日的遊行人數對展現港人抗暴政的決心極為重要。 <br />\n<br />\n註: 派發期間，我們曾被港鐵公司以天橋是私人地方為由阻止，惟有之後改在空地，最後也把所有文宣派到康城街坊手中。<br />\n<br />\n#元旦遊行 #最後機會宣傳 #康城<br />\n<br />\n--- --- --- --- --- --- --- --- --- ---<br />\n革新香港薈社<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/108775563974359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F108775563974359&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=2c4bd397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/108775563974359</a><br />\nTelegram: @hlufc"},{"pid":"9399f5a66d02cd125673952a4cd2599b7e003543","tid":1805684,"uid":21493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"重有上網大把圖可以印去宣傳<br />\n<br /